com.github.wuic.engine.impl.embedded
Class CGBinPacker<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.github.wuic.engine.impl.embedded.CGBinPacker<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
DimensionPacker<T>, Comparator<T>
public final class CGBinPacker<T>
extends Object
implements Comparator<T>, DimensionPacker<T>

This packer is inspired from the grower bin packing algorithm explained by Jakes Gordon to give a position to a set of dimensions in the lowest area.

Comparator interface is implemented to guarantee that dimensions will be packed beginning with the biggest one (width * height).
